-- U.K. Economy Growth Forecasts to Be Revised Lower in OBR Report, FT Says
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-06-14T00:01:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/u-k-economy-growth-forecasts-to-be-cut-in-report-ft-says.html

          
          
             U.K. economic growth forecasts are
to be revised lower by the newly formed Office for Budget
Responsibility, the Financial Times reported, citing people near
the process.  
 The projected overall deficit size is not expected to be
increased greatly by the office when it publishes its report
today, the newspaper said.  
